snippet.title: Hover! (Windows 95) - Levels 14-26
snippet.description:
Playing Hover Levels 14-26.

The game only lets you start out as far as level 16, but you can continue you on beyond that.  After level 16, I think the enemies go back to level 1 intelligence and progress smarter and smarter with each level again, but the number of opponents doesn't reset, there just keeps getting more of them.

There is a 3 level browser game remake of the game with updated graphics at http://hover.ie/
